item>Crosswalked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>III/IVspc</date>
<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Βάσ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ος</unclear> Εὐλογίῳ ἀδε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">λφῷ</supplied> 

    <lb n="2"/>χαίρειν 

    <lb n="3"/>καλῶς ποιήσεις <choice><corr>ὁμιλή<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σας</supplied></corr><sic>ομειλη<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σας</supplied></sic></choice> 

    <lb n="4"/>τῷ Ἀμόι περὶ τῆς οἰκίας τ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">οῦ ἐ</supplied>-

    <lb n="5"/>πιβάλλοντος αὐτῷ μέρ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ους</supplied> 

    <lb n="6"/>καὶ δηλώσας μοι τὴν ποσό-

    <lb n="7"/>τητα <add place="supralinear">τῆς τιμῆς</add> καὶ ὡσαύτως <choice><corr>Ἀπολλω-

    <lb n="8"/>νίῳ</corr><sic>απολλωνιου</sic></choice> καὶ <choice><corr>Θεοδώρῳ</corr><sic>θεοδωρου</sic></choice>· ἀλλ᾽ ὅρα 

    <lb n="9"/>μὴ ἀμελήσῃς, ἄδελφε. ὡς γὰρ 

    <lb n="10"/>οἶδας, ἀπαραίτητός ἐστιν ἡ χ-

    <lb n="11"/>ρεία· νομίζω ὅτι καί σοι κα-

    <lb n="12"/>ταφαίνεται εὔλογον εἶναι 

    <lb n="13"/>τὸ ἀποδημῆσαι, λοιπὸν ἤδη 

    <lb n="14"/>καὶ θερμανθέντων τῶν ἀέ-

    <lb n="15"/>ρων· εἰ οὖν τι ἔχεις ἐν χερσί, 

    <lb n="16"/>διαθοῦ αὐτό, ἵνα, ἐὰν μη-

    <lb n="17"/>δὲν ἐν<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear>ν<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τί</unclear>ον, τῇ δεκάτῃ ἐξορ-

    <lb n="18"/>μήσωμεν· ἐὰν ᾖ σοι ἀβαρές, 

    <lb n="19"/>σκυλεὶς πρὸς Θέονα τὸν σκυ-

    <lb n="20"/>τέα καὶ Γερόντιον ποίησον 

    <lb n="21"/>αὐτοὺς γενέσθαι πρὸς μὲ ἅ-

    <lb n="22"/>μα τῷ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>ὰ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">γρ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">άμμ</unclear>ατά σοι ἐπι-

    <lb n="23"/>φέροντι, καὶ Διοσκουρίδην 

    <lb n="24"/>δὲ τὸν χρυσοχόον· ἐπίστει-

    <lb n="25"/>λον δέ μοι πάντως. 

    <lb n="26"/>ἐρρωσ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">θαί</unclear> σε εὔχομαι, 

    <lb n="27"/>κύριε ἄδελφε, πανοικεὶ 

    <lb n="28"/>ἐπὶ μήκιστον χρόνον. </ab></div><div n="meta.30396" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.30396" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="400" notBefore="201" type="textDate">III - IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.30396" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">34</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">2727</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">30396</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">34</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">2727</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;34;2727" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.30396" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">197</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">XI</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">164</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.30396" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.30396" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl default="NO" subtype="other" type="publication">Tibiletti, Lettere private 19</bibl></div><div n="meta.30396" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl default="NO" lang="it"><head lang="de">Italienisch:</head><bibl default="NO" type="translations">Tibiletti, Lettere private (1979), 19</bibl><bibl default="NO" type="translations">Migliardi, Vita privata e vita pubblica (1992), 94</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.30396" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" full="yes" type="ancientFindspot">Oxyrhynchos</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.30396" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://163.1.169.40/cgi-bin/library?e=d-000-00---0POxy--00-0-0-0prompt-10---4---Document---0-1l--1-en-50---20-about---001-001-1-0utfZz-8-00031-001-1-0utfZz-8-00&amp;a=d&amp;c=POxy&amp;cl=CL5.1.14&amp;d=HASH01d39bff931970545caea35e"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>